title: Goldman Traders Warn Stock Selling Isn’t Over in Choppy Market
description: After rebounding Friday to nearly erase a brutal mid-week slide, US stocks are facing more selling this week from trend-following algorithmic funds, according to Goldman Sachs Group Inc.’s trading desk.
